      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm working on a briefing for an NGO looking to expand operations in the Democratic Republic of the Congo. Can you give me an overview of the primary social tensions in the DRC right now, specifically regarding how the different ethnic groups interact and if there are any major tribal or ethnic risks we should be aware of?",
