    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Looking at the broader picture, how much of this instability is actually due to these deep-seated tribal divisions versus more modern political issues? Like, is it fundamentally a matter of ethnic identity and ancient rivalries, or is there more to it than just \"tribalism\"?",
